column3: Honey: Released February 28, 2007, by the National Agricultural Statistics Service (NASS), Agricultural Statistics Board, U.S. Department of Agriculture.
Honey:  Number of Colonies, Yield, Production, Stocks, Price,
and Value by State and United States, 2006 1/
1/  For producers with 5 or more colonies.  Colonies which produced honey in more than one State were counted in each State.
4/  CT, DE, MD, MA, NH, OK, RI, and SC not published separately to avoid disclosing data for individual operations.
5/  Due to rounding, total colonies multiplied by total yield may not exactly equal production.
